  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.9,
      "text": "Excuse me, sir, I have a question for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 2.3,
      "end": 3.1,
      "text": "How old were you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.3,
      "end": 5.2,
      "text": "Real quick, real quick, how old were you when you became a millionaire?"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.0,
      "end": 8.2,
      "text": "I'm going all over Hong Kong, interviewing the richest people."
    },
    {
      "start": 8.5,
      "end": 9.1,
      "text": "No, no, no, no."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.1,
      "end": 10.1,
      "text": "Hey, one minute, real quick."
    },
    {
      "start": 10.5,
      "end": 10.8,
      "text": "Is that okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 11.3,
      "end": 12.7,
      "text": "How old were you when you became a millionaire?"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.1,
      "end": 15.9,
      "text": "It's an interesting question, because I'm a billionaire."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.5,
      "end": 16.9,
      "text": "You're what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.0,
      "end": 18.0,
      "text": "I'm not a millionaire."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.5,
      "end": 19.0,
      "text": "I'm a billionaire."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.5,
      "end": 20.1,
      "text": "You're a billionaire?"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.4,
      "end": 20.5,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.8,
      "end": 21.2,
      "text": "How old are you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.3,
      "end": 21.8,
      "text": "I'm 34."
    },
    {
      "start": 22.2,
      "end": 23.4,
      "text": "So what age did you become a billionaire?"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.8,
      "end": 25.2,
      "text": "25, I would say 25."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.8,
      "end": 28.2,
      "text": "I built one of the largest blockchains in the world."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.3,
      "end": 28.8,
      "text": "Are you serious?"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.1,
      "end": 29.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 29.2,
      "end": 31.0,
      "text": "Can I interview you off to the side real quick for one minute?"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.3,
      "end": 31.4,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 31.5,
      "end": 33.0,
      "text": "Can you tell me a crazy business story?"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.4,
      "end": 34.0,
      "text": "Yes, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.2,
      "end": 36.2,
      "text": "So I have lunch with Warren Buffett."
    },
    {
      "start": 36.2,
      "end": 37.5,
      "text": "You had lunch with Warren Buffett?"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.6,
      "end": 38.3,
      "text": "Yes, yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.4,
      "end": 38.7,
      "text": "2020."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.4,
      "end": 40.7,
      "text": "How did you get a lunch with Warren Buffett?"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.1,
      "end": 42.7,
      "text": "4.5 million dollars."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.0,
      "end": 45.1,
      "text": "So you paid 4.5 million to get a lunch with Warren Buffett?"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.1,
      "end": 45.7,
      "text": "Yes, yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.8,
      "end": 46.4,
      "text": "It wasn't worth it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.7,
      "end": 48.0,
      "text": "Yes, it totally wasn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.1,
      "end": 49.6,
      "text": "What did Warren Buffett teach you in that lunch?"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.7,
      "end": 53.2,
      "text": "He said be careful with the one you marry."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.6,
      "end": 55.9,
      "text": "You need to make this decision really hard."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.1,
      "end": 56.8,
      "text": "Warren Buffett told you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.8,
      "end": 57.0,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.0,
      "end": 60.0,
      "text": "And I tell him to invest Tesla and Bitcoin."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.3,
      "end": 61.0,
      "text": "Do you earn a lot of Bitcoin?"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.5,
      "end": 63.2,
      "text": "Yes, I personally have a lot."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.4,
      "end": 63.9,
      "text": "A lot of Bitcoin?"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.2,
      "end": 64.3,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.4,
      "end": 66.4,
      "text": "Why are you telling Warren Buffett to invest in Bitcoin?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.8,
      "end": 69.3,
      "text": "The reason Warren Buffett told me not to hold Bitcoin"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.3,
      "end": 71.5,
      "text": "is the reason I invested Bitcoin."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.7,
      "end": 74.6,
      "text": "Crypto and the blockchain is the money for the internet."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.9,
      "end": 78.2,
      "text": "AI and the internet won't understand the traditional finance."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.6,
      "end": 79.9,
      "text": "They won't understand the dollar."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.2,
      "end": 83.0,
      "text": "They will understand Bitcoin and all the cryptocurrency"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.0,
      "end": 86.3,
      "text": "because it's created by the machine language."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.3,
      "end": 89.8,
      "text": "If you want to get into crypto, the best time is now."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.0,
      "end": 92.6,
      "text": "Growing up, did you have any idea that you were going to become a billionaire?"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.0,
      "end": 94.8,
      "text": "For myself, I think 100%."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.8,
      "end": 98.0,
      "text": "But the people knowing me, I think they have no idea."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.3,
      "end": 98.9,
      "text": "I become a billionaire."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.1,
      "end": 100.0,
      "text": "Did you have people that doubted you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.1,
      "end": 100.4,
      "text": "Everybody."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.8,
      "end": 101.1,
      "text": "Everybody?"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.4,
      "end": 101.5,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.7,
      "end": 104.6,
      "text": "Among yourself and all of the billionaires that you've met,"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.9,
      "end": 107.3,
      "text": "what is that one trait that they all have in common?"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.4,
      "end": 110.9,
      "text": "For the one thing, all the billionaires all share for me"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.9,
      "end": 113.1,
      "text": "is they all have their own business."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.4,
      "end": 115.2,
      "text": "So you can't get rich working for somebody else?"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.3,
      "end": 115.7,
      "text": "Exactly."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.7,
      "end": 116.4,
      "text": "What's your name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.6,
      "end": 117.1,
      "text": "Justin Sun."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.4,
      "end": 120.4,
      "text": "Justin Sun, if me and you died tomorrow and you had one more message"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.4,
      "end": 122.3,
      "text": "to leave with the younger generation, what would that be?"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.5,
      "end": 123.0,
      "text": "Buy Bitcoin."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.4,
      "end": 123.9,
      "text": "Buy Bitcoin."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.2,
      "end": 124.7,
      "text": "Buy Bitcoin."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.9,
      "end": 126.8,
      "text": "It's going to become the future currency."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.1,
      "end": 128.1,
      "text": "You've got amazing advice, man."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.3,
      "end": 128.7,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.0,
      "end": 130.0,
      "text": "Justin, I have to ask you."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.2,
      "end": 131.5,
      "text": "I connect with all the billionaires that I need."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.6,
      "end": 132.3,
      "text": "Can I get your contact?"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.5,
      "end": 133.0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.0,
      "end": 133.3,
      "text": "Is that cool?"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.5,
      "end": 134.2,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, totally."
    }
